are product, but I''m so glad I did. It''s made my weekly car washing so much easier and more effective. The results speak for themselves - my car looks showroom fresh every time. Worth every penny!","verified":1,"helpfulCount":18}]', '[{"count":30,"stars":5,"percentage":44},{"count":11,"stars":4,"percentage":16},{"count":7,"stars":3,"percentage":10},{"count":7,"stars":2,"percentage":10},{"count":13,"stars":1,"percentage":20}]', 'Popular', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07VGMKW7S', NULL, NULL, 'USA', 30, 'us', 0, 1, '"2026-03-29T22:32:31.000Z"', '"2026-04-01T23:47:02.000Z"'
