ets/Amazon Listing Images/4-Pack Hose Guide-20260122T171823Z-1-001/about section snall.jpg","label":"ANTI-JAM","description":"Two independently spinning rollers prevent cable or hose jamming. Run multiple hoses and cords simultaneously without interruption!"}],"heroImage":"https://detailguardz.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/assets/Amazon Listing Images/4-Pack Hose Guide-20260122T171823Z-1-001/about section large.jpg","description":"Using a set of Detail Guardz is the most efficient way to work around your vehicle without being interrupted by stubborn hose and cord jams. This 4-pack gives you complete coverage for all four wheels. The roller system allows smooth movement without tugging your hose or cable.","heroImageAlt":"Detail Guardz Hose Guide 4-Pack under tire"}', '[{"sku":"USA-ABDB1DF3-V-BLUE","name":"Blue","image":"https://detailguardz.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/assets/Canada Products/DETAIL GUARDZ - HOSE GUIDE (4PK)/Detail_Guardz_Car_Hose_Guides_-_4_Pack_Blue_d6ccc2fc-4146-4699-bd6f-625d5a7fad15_720x.webp","price":32.99,"value":"blue","amazon_sku":"USA-ABDB1DF3-V-BLUE"},{"sku":"USA-ABDB1DF3-V-BLACK","name":"Black","image":"https://detailguardz.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/assets/Canada Products/DETAIL GUARDZ - HOSE GUIDE (4PK)/Detail_Guardz_Car_Hose_Guides_-_4_Pack_Black_720x.webp","price":32.99,"value":"black","amazon_sku":"USA-ABDB1DF3-V-BLACK"},{"sku":"USA-ABDB1DF3-V-NEON-GREEN","name":"Neon Green","image":"https://detailguardz.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/assets/Canada Products/DETAIL GUARDZ - HOSE GUIDE (4PK)/Detail_Guardz_Car_Hose_Guides_-_4_Pack_Neon-Green_720x.webp","price":32.99,"value":"neon-green","amazon_sku":"USA-ABDB1DF3-V-NEON-GREEN"},{"sku":"USA-ABDB1DF3-V-RED","name":"Red","image":"https://detailguardz.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/assets/Canada Products/DETAIL GUARDZ - HOSE GUIDE (4PK)/Detail_Guardz_Car_Hose_Guides_-_4_Pack_Red_720x.webp","price":32.99,"value":"red","amazon_sku":"USA-ABDB1DF3-V-RED"},{"sku":"USA-ABDB1DF3-V-YELLOW","name":"Yellow","imag