themselves - my car looks showroom fresh every time. Worth every penny!","verified":1,"helpfulCount":18}]', '[{"count":423,"stars":5,"percentage":75},{"count":85,"stars":4,"percentage":15},{"count":34,"stars":3,"percentage":6},{"count":17,"stars":2,"percentage":3},{"count":5,"stars":1,"percentage":1}]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'both', 0, 1, '"2026-03-29T22:32:31.000Z"', '"2026-04-01T23:47:02.000Z"'
